ricity bill of &ldquo;Yip Foo&rdquo; (葉虎) with registered address in Nam Pin Wai was also discovered. The name is shared by a senior official of Chinese Liaison office responsible for the region, suggesting China&rsquo;s involvement in the terrorist attack on 21/7. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/scmp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fscmp&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=41cf926b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/scmp</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/business\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbusiness&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=5c3fd9c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/business</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/NewYorker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNewYorker&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=c53137e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/NewYorker</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AJEnglish\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAJEnglish&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=45a682c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/AJEnglish</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/guardian\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fguardian&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=2465f4ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/guardian</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SkyNews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSkyNews&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=0065ad54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SkyNews</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nytimes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnytimes&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=389e7869\" data-auto-link 